text: "It's Corn" is a pop song by The Gregory Brothers that remixes and samples portions of an interview of Tariq, nicknamed "Corn Kid" on Recess Therapy. It is also an internet meme. The governor of South Dakota, Kristi Noem, declared September 3 as "Official Corn-bassador Tariq Day".https://archive.today/20220923015947/https://www.nytimes.com/2022/09/21/style/corn- kid-tariq-tiktok.html ==References== Category:Pop songs Category:2022 songs Category:Internet memes
